This is a repost of issue JRA-3923. JRA-3923 was mistakenly closed as a "duplicate" of JRA-3101.  This is *not* a duplicate of JRA-3101.

To paraphrase JRA-3923,  it would be extremely useful if you could create a filter that shows you all issues with *links* of a particular type.  For example, it would be useful if I could create a filter that showed me all issues that had links of type "depends" or of issues that had links of type "relates".

I'm fairly certain that it was a mistake to close JRA-3923 as a duplicate of JRA-3101 -careful reading of the two issues should reveal the distinction.

