We have users that work with very large issues and, upon commenting on an issue, would prefer to be taken to their comment instead of to the top of the issue they commented on.  Please add a user preference for:

Display After Comment: "Issue" | "Comment"

The first option, "Issue" would follow the current behavior of taking you to the URL of the issue just commented on.  The second option, "Comment", would load the URL for the comment "permalink"  for the newly added comment.

